headline: BMO Believes Intuit (INTU) Had Strong Start to FY2026 Driven by Credit Karma, QBO Ecosystem Strength
summary: Intuit Inc. (NASDAQ:INTU) is one of the most profitable tech stocks to buy. Earlier on November 21, BMO Capital analyst Daniel Jester lowered the firm’s price target on Intuit to $810 from $870 but kept an Outperform rating on the shares.
